g Company are proud parents who will stop at nothing for the good of their offspring.'),(910,15,'_partners-partners_0_partners-partners-more','field_548f50724dd5c'),(911,15,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-link','http://www.lnf.com.br/'),(912,15,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-link','field_548f4fd04dd58'),(913,15,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-image','300'),(914,15,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-image','field_548f502d4dd59'),(915,15,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-header','Growing our knowledge and our reach.'),(916,15,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-header','field_548f50394dd5a'),(917,15,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-text','At Haas, we are always looking to enhance the quality of the hops we grow through better technology, processes and efficiencies. That’s why we partner with LNF Latino Americana. Founded in 1987 and active in various biotech industries, LNF is a family-owned and -operated company that was built on the commitment of delivering highly qualified technical support to companies looking for high product quality and process optimization.  '),(918,15,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-text','field_548f505c4dd5b'),(919,15,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-more','The Brewing division of LNF specializes in hops and works closely with the Barth-Haas Group to develop our presence in the Brazilian market through a very close technical and commercial cooperation. '),(920,15,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-more','field_548f50724dd5c'),(921,15,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-link','http://www.willamettevalleyhops.com/'),(922,15,'_partners-partners_2_partners-partners-link','field_548f4fd04dd58'),(923,15,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-image','144'),(924,15,'_partners-partners_2_partners-partners-image','field_548f502d4dd59'),(925,15,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-header',' You don’t have to be big to get Haas hops. But you do have to think big.'),(926,15,'_partners-part