now yours. Because we believe that great service comes from not just knowing what you need, but why you need it.'),(2224,270,'_why-haas-reasons_4_why-haas-reasons-text','field_548f1fa12da24'),(2225,270,'why-haas-reasons_4_why-haas-reasons-icon','96'),(2226,270,'_why-haas-reasons_4_why-haas-reasons-icon','field_548f1f922da23'),(2227,270,'why-haas-reasons_5_why-haas-reasons-header','PASSION'),(2228,270,'_why-haas-reasons_5_why-haas-reasons-header','field_548f1f882da22'),(2229,270,'why-haas-reasons_5_why-haas-reasons-text','Haas is not just a supplier, we are breeders, growers – even brewers – who for generations have helped brewers discover their next great flavor.'),(2230,270,'_why-haas-reasons_5_why-haas-reasons-text','field_548f1fa12da24'),(2231,270,'why-haas-reasons_5_why-haas-reasons-icon','97'),(2232,270,'_why-haas-reasons_5_why-haas-reasons-icon','field_548f1f922da23'),(2233,270,'why-haas-reasons','6'),(2234,270,'_why-haas-reasons','field_548f1f362da21'),(2235,271,'contact-header','LET\'S TALK HOPS.'),(2236,271,'_contact-header','field_548f230add4d4'),(2237,271,'contact-text','Whether you need help finding a hop, placing an order or making a reservation at the Innovations Brewery, give us a call at 1-509-469-4000 or fill out the form.'),(2238,271,'_contact-text','field_548f2319dd4d5'),(2239,271,'contact-sections_0_contact-sections-header','INNOVATIONS CENTER'),(2240,271,'_contact-sections_0_contact-sections-header','field_548f23b6dd4d7'),(2241,271,'contact-sections_0_contact-sections-text','John I. Haas, Inc \r\n1600 River Road \r\nYakima, WA 98902 \r\n+1-509-469-4000'),(2242,271,'_contact-sections_0_contact-sections-text','field_548f24902e131'),(2243,271,'contact-sections_1_contact-sections-header','HEADQUARTERS'),(2244,271,'_contact-sections_1_contact-sections-header','field_548f23b6dd4d7'),(2245,271,'contact-sections_1_contact-sections-text','John I. Haas, Inc \r\n5185 MacArthur Blvd. N.W. \r\nSuite 300 \r\nWashington, D.C. 20016 \r\n+ 1 202-777-XXXX'),(2246