ility that provides repeatable, flexible and scalable brewing capabilities. And that’s exactly what you get with the Innovations Brewery. <strong><a href=\"http://shotgunflatdev.com/ongoing/HAAS3/#\">READ MORE</a></strong>'),(2647,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_0_resources-innovations-brewery-text','field_548f481fd88a3'),(2648,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_0_resources-innovations-brewery-image','128'),(2649,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_0_resources-innovations-brewery-image','field_548f482cd88a4'),(2650,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_1_resources-innovations-brewery-header','IMAGINE WHAT YOU COULD BREW.'),(2651,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_1_resources-innovations-brewery-header','field_548f4808d88a2'),(2652,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_1_resources-innovations-brewery-text','At Haas, we celebrate the passion and creativity of those dedicated to brewing great beer. And our research brewery is one of the ways we help that creativity happen. It starts with our sophisticated, state-of-the-art equipment and control system that allows you to refine a recipe and repeat it batch after batch. Next comes flexibility — the key to innovation. The Haas Innovations Brewery offers you a highly controlled, scientific environment in which to brew, test and adjust your recipes to get the perfect brew. Finally, there’s scalability. Our research brewery provides an unparalleled scalable brewing experience, which means you can reduce the time and uncertainty often associated with new brews and get your next brewing creation to market faster and more efficiently.'),(2653,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_1_resources-innovations-brewery-text','field_548f481fd88a3'),(2654,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_1_resources-innovations-brewery-image','127'),(2655,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_1_resources-innovations-brewery-image','field_548f482cd88a4'),(2656,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_2_resources-innovations-brewery-header','HERE’S TO YOUR SUCCESS'),(2657,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_2_resources-innovations-brewery-header','field_548f4808d88a2'),(2658,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_2_resources-innovations-brewery-text','At Haas, our mission is your success. Whether you’re looking to test one of our new varieties or one of your latest recipes, the Haas Innovations Brewery will help you achieve it. The Haas research brewery also allows you to test our new products and see how we can deliver the same great flavors you seek without having to use as many hops (or dollars, for that matter). In addition to giving you a place to brew, our research brewery includes a state-of-the-art laboratory that gives you the advantage of the latest hop and beer analysis technology. You also get the experience and expertise of our technical staff and brewmaster Virgil McDonald who help you get the most out of the product development process. To learn more or to reserve a brewing session, call 509-469-4000<strong>.</strong> And get ready to test, tweak, taste and toast your next great brew.'),(2659,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_2_resources-innovations-brewery-text','field_548f481fd88a3'),(2660,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_2_resources-innovations-brewery-image','129'),(2661,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_2_resources-innovations-brewery-image','field_548f482cd88a4'),(2662,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_3_resources-innovations-brewery-header','INNOVATIONS BREWERY FEATURES:'),(2663,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_3_resources-innovations-brewery-header','field_548f4808d88a2'),(2664,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_3_resources-innovations-brewery-text','<ul>\r\n	<li>2.5 hl 5 vessel state-of-the-art brew house with 10 and 30 liter hop dosing vessels</li>\r\n	<li>A brew house control system with customizable recipe and extensive data collection</li>\r\n	<li>21 unitank fermentation and conditioning system capable of 1.25 and 2.5 hl brews</li>\r\n	<li>Beer filtration capabilities including diatomaceous earth and depth filter</li>\r\n	<li>Krones bottling system with double pre-evacuation &amp; CO2 pressurization</li>\r\n	<li>Precision malt milling (4 roll) and adjunct preparation</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory analysis for hops and beer</li>\r\n</ul>'),(2665,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_3_resources-innovations-brewery-text','field_548f481fd88a3'),(2666,294,'resources-innovations-brewery_3_resources-innovations-brewery-image','130'),(2667,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery_3_resources-innovations-brewery-image','field_548f482cd88a4'),(2668,294,'resources-innovations-brewery','4'),(2669,294,'_resources-innovations-brewery','field_548f47c0d88a1'),(2670,294,'resources-hops-academy_0_resources-hops-academy-header','HOPS. THERE’S MORE\r\nTHAN MEETS THE NOSE.'),(2671,294,'_resources-hops-academy_0_resources-hops-academy-header','field_548f487dd88a6'),(2672,294,'resources-hops-academy_0_resources-hops-academy-text','It seems like the more you know about hops, the more there is to learn. That’s the thinking behind the Barth-Haas Hops Academy — a formal training program for brewers designed to open up a world of possibilities in the use, effects, and impact of this special brewing ingredient. In addition to helping brewers develop distinctive high-quality beers, the Hops Academy helps you improve process efficiencies and reduce waste.\r\n\r\nThe Hops Academy helps both new, experienced and even master brewers understand more about the complexities of hops and the way they interact with each other — as well as other beer ingredients — to create unique styles, flavors and aromas. To learn more about the Barth-Haas Hops Academy or to reserve a spot in an upcoming session, please visit <a href=\"http://www.hopsacademy.com/en\">http://www.hopsacademy.com/en</a>'),(2673,294,'_resources-hops-academy_0_resources-hops-academy-text','field_548f48a2d88a7'),(2674,294,'resources-hops-academy_0_resources-hops-academy-image','131'),(2675,294,'_resources-hops-academy_0_resources-hops-academ