onstate.edu/video/fermentation-science-oregon-state-university'),(2943,297,'_resources-other_3_resources-other-text','field_548f4931d88ac'),(2944,297,'resources-other_4_resources-other-link',''),(2945,297,'_resources-other_4_resources-other-link','field_548f4b1ba29aa'),(2946,297,'resources-other_4_resources-other-image','293'),(2947,297,'_resources-other_4_resources-other-image','field_548f48fed88aa'),(2948,297,'resources-other_4_resources-other-header','HOP GROWERS OF AMERICA'),(2949,297,'_resources-other_4_resources-other-header','field_548f4916d88ab'),(2950,297,'resources-other_4_resources-other-text','Hop Growers of America is a non-profit association that represents and promotes the interests of U.S. growers both domestically and internationally. As the national organization, HGA provides support, coordination and communication to growers, brewers and the world hop industry in areas of common interest, including; marketing statistics, promotion, education, and research.  \r\nhttp://www.usahops.org'),(2951,297,'_resources-other_4_resources-other-text','field_548f4931d88ac'),(2952,297,'resources-other','5'),(2953,297,'_resources-other','field_548f48e1d88a9'),(2954,298,'contact-header','LET\'S TALK HOPS.'),(2955,298,'_contact-header','field_548f230add4d4'),(2956,298,'contact-text','Thanks for coming to our website. If you don’t know where to start, this\r\nis a good place. Just fill out the form and we’ll get back to you right\r\naway. If you know who you want to talk to, just give us their name and\r\nwe’ll have him or her get right back to you. If you need immediate help\r\nfinding a hop, placing an order or making a reservation at the\r\nInnovations Brewery, give us a call at 1-509-469-4000.'),(2957,298,'_contact-text','field_548f2319dd4d5'),(2958,298,'contact-sections_0_contact-sections-header','INNOVATIONS CENTER'),(2959,298,'_contact-sections_0_contact-sections-header','field_548f23b6dd4d7'),(2960,298,'contact-sections_0_contact-sections-text','John I. Haas,