reated_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(8512,791,'_thumbnail_id','800'),(8515,804,'_edit_lock','1429196014:1'),(8516,804,'_edit_last','1'),(8544,811,'name','Daniel Fanha'),(8545,811,'email','daniel.fanha@connecton-mkt.com.br'),(8546,811,'website','www.connecton-mkt.com.br'),(8547,811,'subject','Make an Innovations Brewery Reservation'),(8548,811,'comment','Prezados,\r\nSolicito o contato do departamento de marketing para apresentar a empresa Connect ON Marketing de Eventos.\r\nNo aguardo!\r\nAtt,\r\nDaniel Fanha'),(8549,812,'_edit_lock','1427995777:3'),(8550,812,'_edit_last','3'),(8551,813,'name','Marek Szymczyk'),(8552,813,'email','marek.szymczyk@bnsflogistics.com'),(8553,813,'website','www.bnsflogistics.com'),(8554,813,'subject','Make an Innovations Brewery Reservation'),(8555,813,'comment','Good morning,\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is Mark with BNSF Logistics, we provide OTR , IM and LTL  transportation services to variety of customers nationwide at some very competitive rates and I would love to offer these same services to You.  We have over 30K contracted carriers in our portfolio so there isn’t a shipment that we cannot \r\n\r\nhandle.  BNSF is all about service and our on time delivery exceeds 98% nationwide so whether you need some help with your inbound freight (raw materials) or your outbound freight (finished goods) we can certainly assist.  Our unique and signature characteristic is the “1-point contact feature” we \r\n\r\noffer and what this means is that regardless if You award me with 5 loads per week or 25 loads per week I would still be the only person You would ever have to deal with @ BNSF, no 1-800 numbers that never get answered or emails that never get replied.  I am available to my customers pretty much 24/7.\r\n\r\nWe are not the “one man broker operation” who works out of his house, the kind of broker that goes out of business when the first significant claim comes around.  We are a non-asset based 3PL, but unlike other non-asset based 3PL we are backed by Berkshire Hathaway, have legal liability insurance with \r\n\r\nlimits above statutory requirements, will indemnify our customers for our carriers, and warrant that all cargo claims for which our retained carriers are adjudged legally liable will be paid.  Please reply to this message as soon as possible as I would like to send you additional information about BNSF and who we \r\n\r\nare.  You can also go to our website @ www.bnsflogistics.com to get a better idea about us.  \r\n\r\n\r\nThank You and have a great day\r\n'),(8556,814,'name','Jesse Friedman'),(8557,814,'email','jesse@almanacbeer.com'),(8558,814,'website','almanacbeer.com'),(8559,814,'subject','Buy hops or hop products'),(8560,814,'comment','Howdy!  I\'m interested in Citra hop contract, ideally starting with the 2015 harvest.  Do you have any availability? \r\n\r\nThanks!\r\n\r\n- Jesse \r\nAlmanac Beer Co'),(8561,815,'name','Ryan Graham'),(8562,815,'email','rgraham@track7brewing.com'),(8563,815,'website','www.track7brewing.com'),(8564,815,'subject','Buy hops or hop products'),(8565,815,'comment','Hello,\r\n\r\nUp to this point, I believe our individual hop purchases/contracts have been too small to meet Haas\' size requirements.  However, as we are starting to hit estimated barrelage of 10,000 this year (2015), 20,000 next year (2016) and 30,000 the following year (2017) I believe our purchasing requirements should now align.  Can someone from Haas please either call or email me to discuss hop availability for contracting?  My cell phone number is 909-991-9397.  Or my email is graham@track7brewing.com.  I sincerely appreciate your time and look forward to speaking with someone.  Best,\r\n\r\nRyan Graham\r\nOwner/Brewmaster\r\nTrack 7 Brewing Company\r\nSacramento, CA'),(8566,816,'name','Bill Moore'),(8567,816,'email','bmoore@lancasterbrewing.com'),(8568,816,'websit