standing of the entire brewing process from hop to glass. Prior to joining Haas, Dean was Business Unit Manager of our sister company Simply Hops Limited based in England. He focused on developing sales in the United Kingdom and the European Union craft brewing sector.'),(9146,921,'_team-description','field_54908498ead1e'),(9147,921,'team-moment','when the brewer receives more than just a hop contract, but a strategic partner who can help develop their next great beer!'),(9148,921,'_team-moment','field_549084bbead1f'),(9149,922,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/Monshing.jpg'),(9150,922,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1865;s:6:\"height\";i:2359;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2015/06/Monshing.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"Monshing-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"Monshing-237x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:237;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Monshing-810x1024.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:810;s:6:\"height\";i:1024;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:10:\"blog-thumb\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"Monshing-508x193.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:508;s:6:\"height\";i:193;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";d:5.5999999999999996447286321199499070644378662109375;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:10:\"NIKON 1 J1\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:1428672386;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:2:\"30\";s:3:\"iso\";s:3:\"800\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:4:\"0.02\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:1;}}'),(9152,923,'_edit_lock','1441806646:6'),(9153,923,'_edit_last','6'),(9154,924,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/JohnGorman.jpg'),(9155,924,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:752;s:6:\"height\";i:1068;s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"2015/06/JohnGorman.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\