elivers a wealth of information to his customers and he is widely recognized for exemplary levels of service as well.'),(9160,923,'_team-description','field_54908498ead1e'),(9161,923,'team-moment','when a brewer understands that our only goal is to provide the products, services and innovation that help them overcome their challenges and be successful.'),(9162,923,'_team-moment','field_549084bbead1f'),(9163,925,'_edit_lock','1441978329:6'),(9164,925,'_edit_last','6'),(9165,926,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/ALFREDO.jpg'),(9166,926,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:2553;s:6:\"height\";i:2502;s:4:\"file\";s:19:\"2015/06/ALFREDO.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:19:\"ALFREDO-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:19:\"ALFREDO-300x294.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:294;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"ALFREDO-1024x1004.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:1004;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:10:\"blog-thumb\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:19:\"ALFREDO-508x193.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:508;s:6:\"height\";i:193;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";d:5.5999999999999996447286321199499070644378662109375;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:10:\"NIKON 1 J1\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:1423558996;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:2:\"30\";s:3:\"iso\";s:3:\"800\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:4:\"0.01\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:1;}}'),(9168,925,'team-position','Director of International Sales'),(9169,925,'_team-position','field_54908460ead1d'),(9170,925,'team-description','Originally part of the Barth-Haas Group in Germany, Alfredo Almeida joined John I. Haas, Inc. in 2009 as Director of International Sales, covering the Latin American market.  Prior to joining Haas, Alfredo worked for AmBev in Brazil, Molson Canada, Pernod Ricard Canada and the Growing Power Group in Canada, holding various positions in production such as a Brewmaster, Beer Production Manager, Distillery &amp; Grain Operations Manager and positions in General Management. Alfredo holds a Bachelors Degree in Chemical Engineering from the Polytechnic School of the University of Sao Paulo, a Masters Degree in Brewing from the VLB Berlin, and an MBA from Saint Mary’s University in Nova Scotia, Canada.'),(9171,925,'_team-description','field_54908498ead1e'),(9172,925,'team-moment','when you can combine your technical knowledge with your business knowledge to bring solutions and opportunities to new markets and new partners.'),(9173,925,'_team-moment','field_549084bbead1f'),(9176,928,'name','Abraham salazar'),(9177,928,'email','abrahamsalazar@cuitlahuc.com'),(9178,928,'website','www.cuitlahuac.com'),(9179,928,'subject','Make an Innovations Brewery Reservation'),(9180,928,'comment','Buen día,\r\nActualmente soy un cliente suyo de México. Hemos recibido una mala atención por parte de ustedes y quien esta al contacto con nosotros es imposible nos dé respuestas objetivas de nuestros productos. Agradeceré si alguien de ustedes se interesa por mi correo se comunique conmigo y podamos solucionar los problemas actuales. Gracias '),(9181,929,'partners-header','HAAS. WHERE BREWING IS A TEAM SPORT'),(9182,929,'_partners-header','field_548f4f6c4dd56'),(9183,929,'partners-partners_0_partners-partners-link','http://www.hopbreeding.com'),(9184,929,'_partners-partners_0_partners-partners-link','field_548f4fd04dd58'),(9185,929,'partners-partners_0_partners-partners-image','146'),(9186,929,'_partners-partners_0_partners-partners-image','field_548f502d4dd59'),(9187,929,'partners-partners_0_partners-partners-header','Where new beer flavors are born.'),(9188,929,'_partners-partners_0_partners-partners-header','field_548f50394dd5a'),(9189,929,'partners-partners_0_partners-partners-text','Citra®, Mosaic®, and Equinox® — we all recognize these names as the hops behind (or, more accurately, inside) some of craft brewing’s most well known beers. But what you may not know is that these varieties were created from scratch by the Hops Breeding Company LLC, a joint venture between Haas and Select Botanicals LLC. '),(9190,929,'_partners-partners_0_partners-partners-text','field_548f505c4dd5b'),(9191,929,'partners-partners_0_partners-partners-more','Coming up with new aromas and flavors is a big part of what Haas contributes to the world brewing community. And one of the key contributors to these creations is our long-time master hop breeder, Gene Probasco. Gene and his agronomic team oversee more than 30 acres of experimental hops just waiting to be discovered.  The Hop Breeding Company conducts about 50 crosses of male and female hop parents each year, resulting in more than 20,000 offspring, all potentially becoming a commercial variety someday in the future.  While only a handful make it to an elite status and get christened with a name instead of a number, Gene and the Hop Breeding Company are proud parents who will stop at nothing for the good of their offspring.'),(9192,929,'_partners-partners_0_partners-partners-more','field_548f50724dd5c'),(9193,929,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-link','http://www.lnf.com.br/'),(9194,929,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-link','field_548f4fd04dd58'),(9195,929,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-image','300'),(9196,929,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-image','field_548f502d4dd59'),(9197,929,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-header','Growing our knowledge and our reach.'),(9198,929,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-header','field_548f50394dd5a'),(9199,929,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-text','At Haas, we are always looking to enhance the quality of the hops we grow through better technology, processes and efficiencies. That’s why we partner with LNF Latino Americana. Founded in 1987 and active in various biotech industries, LNF is a family-owned and -operated company that was built on the commitment of delivering highly qualified technical support to companies looking for high product quality and process optimization.  '),(9200,929,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-text','field_548f505c4dd5b'),(9201,929,'partners-partners_1_partners-partners-more','The Brewing division of LNF specializes in hops and works closely with the Barth-Haas Group to develop our presence in the Brazilian market through a very close technical and commercial cooperation. '),(9202,929,'_partners-partners_1_partners-partners-more','field_548f50724dd5c'),(9203,929,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-link','http://www.willamettevalleyhops.com/'),(9204,929,'_partners-partners_2_partners-partners-link','field_548f4fd04dd58'),(9205,929,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-image','144'),(9206,929,'_partners-partners_2_partners-partners-image','field_548f502d4dd59'),(9207,929,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-header',' You don’t have to be big to get Haas hops. But you do have to think big.'),(9208,929,'_partners-partners_2_partners-partners-header','field_548f50394dd5a'),(9209,929,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-text','Just because you’re a small brewery doesn’t mean you shouldn’t be able to get your hands on high-quality Haas hops. And thanks to our partnership with Willamette Valley Hops LLC, you can. '),(9210,929,'_partners-partners_2_partners-partners-text','field_548f505c4dd5b'),(9211,929,'partners-partners_2_partners-partners-more','Willamette Valley Hops is an Oregon-based family-owned premium hop distributor, which specializes in the special needs of the craft industry.  Located in the heart of Oregon’s Willamette Valley hop growing region, Bruce Wolf, the company’s founder and CEO, leads a passionate sales team and production staff to provide over 50 different domestic and foreign hop varieties to brewers worldwide. The partnership between John I. Haas and Willamette Valley Hops provides an effective and efficient means to give small brewers access to the best hops in the world.'),(9212,929,'_partners-partners_2_partners-partners-more','field_548f50724dd5c'),(9213,929,'partners-partners','3'),(9214,929,'_partners-partners','field_548f4fab4dd57'),(9215,931,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/Roy.jpg'),(9216,931,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:378;s:6:\"height\";i:288;s:4:\"file\";s:15:\"2015/06/Roy.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:15:\"Roy-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:15:\"Roy-300x229.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:229;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:10:\"blog-thumb\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:15:\"Roy-378x193.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:378;s:6:\"height\";i:193;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(9218,932,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/Tim_Kostelecky1.jpg'),(9219,932,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:378;s:6:\"height\";i:288;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2015/06/Tim_Kostelecky1.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Tim_Kostelecky1-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Tim_Kostelecky1-300x229.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:229;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:10:\"blog-thumb\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Tim_Kostelecky1-378x193.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:378;s:6:\"height\";i:193;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:1