d services of beer, l have a list of the dealers, resellers and buyers, because l work more than 10 years prospecting importers and dealers in general.\r\n\r\n     I do business, law and marketing assistance to help your company to do business in Brazil.\r\n\r\n     I do tourist assistance and l can make city tour to Sao Paulo city, to the beaches as Santos, Guaruja or any other place.\r\n\r\n     l would like very much to work to your company at the trade show or in another opportunity.\r\n\r\n     Please contact me by mobile and WhatsApp  +5511-99606-7834, in Sao Paulo dial just 99606-7834 or 011996067834 .\r\nE-mails: appollosheila1@gmail.com, appollosheila@terra.com.br\r\n\r\nThank you for your attention\r\n\r\nRegards\r\n\r\n\r\nSheila Appollo cel +5511-99606-7834 appollosheila@terra.com.br,\r\nappollosheila1@gmail.com\r\n\r\n      Meu nome e Sheila Appollo, sou Interprete em Ingles, Espanhol, Portugues. Posso dar assistencia em transportar estrangeiros e expositores do aeroporto para hotel, feira, reuniões etc.\r\n.\r\n      Também trabalho com pesquisa de mercado a mais de 10 anos na area de produtos e servicos de cervejaria ou com empresas de qualquer area.\r\n\r\n      Posso fazer city tour na cidade de São Paulo, nas praias como Santos, Guarujá ou em outros lugares.\r\n\r\n      Gostaria muito de trabalhar para a sua empresa na Feira ou em outra oportunidade.\r\n\r\n      Favor entrar em contato comigo pelo cel +5511-99606-7834 .\r\n\r\n\r\nEstimado(a) Señor / Señora\r\n\r\nSoy una traductora portugués, español e inglés, hacemos un trabajo de asesorar los expositores adelante, durante e después de la Feira y para transporte tamben .Me gustaría trabajar en la Feira – São Paulo – Brazil o in otra oportunidad.\r\n\r\nTeléfono para contacto +5511-99606-7834  appollosheila1@gmail.co\r\n\r\nGracias por su atención\r\n\r\n'),(9293,952,'name','Tom Sparling'),(9294,952,'email','tomsparling@drivevalley.com'),(9295,952,'website','Yakima SouthWest Rotary'),(9296,952,'subject','Make an Innovations Brewery Reservation'),(9297,952,'comment','This is an invitation to John N. Forte to come speak to the local SouthWest Rotary Club here in Yakima. He recently presented to the Downtown Rotary Club and our club was wondering if he might consider also speaking to ours. We meet on Tuesday afternoons at 4:30pm at Zesta Cucinas here in Yakima. Please forward this message to him. He can respond to my email address above. Thank you.'),(9298,953,'name','bill russell'),(9299,953,'email','bill.russell@buzzardsbrew.com'),(9300,953,'website','buzzardsbrew.com'),(9301,953,'subject','Buy hops or hop products'),(9302,953,'comment','We\'re looking for samples (and are willing to pay) of the following:\r\nAdmiral\r\nBor\r\nBullion\r\nCascade\r\nCentennial\r\nChallenger\r\nChinook\r\nCluster\r\nComet\r\nElla\r\nEroica\r\nGalaxy\r\nGlacier\r\nGreenburg\r\nHallertauer\r\nHersbrucker\r\nLiberty\r\nMagnum\r\nMerkur\r\nMillenium\r\nNewport\r\nNorthern Brewer\r\nOpal\r\nPhoenix\r\nPilot\r\nSantian\r\nSaphir\r\nSladek\r\nSmaragd\r\nSticklebract\r\nSummit\r\nSybilla\r\nTarget\r\nTettnang\r\nTillicum\r\nTomahawk\r\nTopaz\r\nTradition\r\nUltra\r\nVanguard\r\nWarrior\r\nWGV\r\nZythos\r\nMuch thanks,\r\nBill Russell\r\nbill.russell@buzzardsbrew.com\r\n774-201-9297'),(9303,954,'name','Peter Ford'),(9304,954,'email','pete@alynnmorganbrewing.com'),(9305,954,'website','Under construction'),(9306,954,'subject','Buy hops or hop products'),(9307,954,'comment','Recently graduated from the American Brewer\'s Guild with Steve Parks in Middlebury, VT. Currently a 15 BBL brewery-in-planning with open date projected at Spring 2016. Would like to discuss hop contract for pellets and CO2 extracts. Also, had an opportunity to view your Barth-Haas Hops Companion 2nd Edition at the ABG and would like to know how I can get a copy. I look forward to hearing from you.\r\nCheers!\r\nPete Ford \r\nAlynn Morgan Brewing Company\r\n4 Taylor Lane\r\nWallingford, CT   06492\r\npete@alynnmorgan