ickerpublishing.com'),(9637,1030,'website','www.beverage-master.com'),(9638,1030,'subject','Request More Information'),(9639,1030,'comment','I am with the National Publication Beverage Master Craft Spirits & Brew Magazine, I hope we could talk about possible marketing in Advertising and also Articles. Please contact me for further information. 515-302-8128\r\n\r\nCheers,\r\n\r\nMichael Moore\r\n'),(9640,1022,'_oembed_90f6a4276fadb95c41b32ac979acc095','{{unknown}}'),(9641,1032,'name','Brad Harris'),(9642,1032,'email','bd2004@me.com'),(9643,1032,'website','Royston Nano Brewery - Facebook page'),(9644,1032,'subject','Request More Information'),(9645,1032,'comment','Hello.  I am an avid home brewer with a one barrel system in my garage, AKA the Royston Nano Brewery.  I am a Family Physician by day, charitable brewer by night and weekend.  My now 6 1/2 year old daughter Linden had leukaemia, and so now my passion for beer has morphed to a passion for brewing beer for charity.  I\'ve raised around $25 000 while curing cancer in my daughter and doctoring  my 1700 strong flock of patients.  We live on Vancouver Island in BC and next week hope to be driving through Yakima.  Can we stop by your shop, see the hop fields (this early hop season must have them pretty close to harvest - my Zeus and Centennial bines are looking nice right now up here in the north) talk beer, hops and maybe purchase something special to take back home?'),(9646,1033,'_edit_lock','1441288367:6'),(9647,1033,'_edit_last','6'),(9648,1034,'_wp_attached_file','2015/08/karl-strauss-mosaic-session-ale-0afc89f5-e1439574559114.jpeg'),(9649,1034,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:500;s:6:\"height\";i:342;s:4:\"file\";s:68:\"2015/08/karl-strauss-mosaic-session-ale-0afc89f5-e1439574559114.jpeg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:53:\"karl-strauss-mosaic-session-ale-0afc89f5-150x150.jpeg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medi