'),(9874,1081,'_edit_last','1'),(9875,1082,'name','Julian Healey'),(9876,1082,'email','julian@hopslist.com'),(9877,1082,'website','www.hopslist.com'),(9878,1082,'subject','Request More Information'),(9879,1082,'comment','Good morning,\r\n\r\nI hope this email find you well!\r\n\r\nSince launching Hopslist.com 18 months ago, we\'ve steadily grown into a widely used resource by brewers internationally as a go-to source for hops info - hopefully you\'ve heard of us. Occasionally, we get contacted by commercial brewers looking to acquire production-scale orders of hops.\r\n\r\nFor example, we\'ve previously received an inquiry from Beyond the Pale in Ottawa, Canada looking for a yearly supply of Galaxy. To date, I have referred these requests to our website sponsors, which unfortunately being homebrewer focused, are severely ill-equipped to fulfill 400lb+ orders!\r\n\r\nYou guys on the other hand clearly are equipped to deal with purchases of this scale. As such, I wanted to reach out and see if you\'d be interested in us referring this business your way in some official capacity.\r\n\r\nAs we grow, I would only expect these requests to become more frequent.\r\n\r\nIf this is of interest, please feel free to get me anytime on my cell (+61 411 685 687) or via email for a chat.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nJulian'),(9880,1083,'name','Ryan'),(9881,1083,'email','Ryan@skewedbrew.com'),(9882,1083,'website','Www.skewedbrew.com'),(9883,1083,'subject','Buy hops or hop products'),(9884,1083,'comment','Looking at getting some hop contracts can I get a list of availability and price. Also can I get a catalogue of your other products as well as a credit or account application. Thanks'),(9885,1084,'name','Scott Houmes'),(9886,1084,'email','scott@silvercitybrewery.com'),(9887,1084,'website','www.silvercitybrewery.com'),(9888,1084,'subject','Buy hops or hop products'),(9889,1084,'comment','Hello,\r\n\r\nI am looking to see if we can start a business relationship.  Can you have your Pacific 