website','www.ormondbuilders.com'),(10118,1114,'subject','Request More Information'),(10119,1114,'comment','Saw a note about your future building plans for a new facility near Yakima.  \r\n\r\nPlease keep us in mind if and when things start to progress to the design and construction stage. We’ve done work in the Tri-Cities / Yakima area would be happy to be able to help you out with any of your construction needs.   \r\n\r\nNicholas Contos\r\nOrmond Builders, Inc.\r\nChief Estimator\r\nPhone: (208) 524-1422\r\nFax (208) 524-7488\r\nncontos@ormondbuilders.com\r\nwww.ormondbuilders.com\r\nP.O. Box 1841\r\nIdaho Falls, ID\r\n');
